high_descs: Head rotate and turn left to the cabinet.
Pick the tomato from the cup-board.
Head rotate and turn right to the microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave oven and pick it back.
Head rotate and turn right to the coffeetable.
Head rotate and turn right to the coffeetable and place the tomato on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: To place the tomato on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around to reach the rightmost cabinet on top of the microwave.
Pick up the tomato from the cabinet.
Turn left to reach the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave and take it out.
Turn left to reach the passage and enter the room on the right to reach the coffeetable.
Put the tomato on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated tomato on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, hang a right and go to the cabinet, turn left at the end of the cabinet.
Open the cupboard on the top and pick up the tomato from it.
Turn left and head straight, turn to the microwave on your right.
Place the tomato inside the microwave, then remove it from the microwave.

Turn left and proceed to the far end of the kitchen. Then, turn right and proceed straight, hang a right, and enter the room. Finally, turn left, right, left, right, and then proceed towards the coffeetable.
Place the tomato on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Heating tomato and placing it on a CoffeeTable.
